creator: Mary Ann H. T. Bigelow
description:
LibriVox recording of The Kings and Queens of England with Other Poems by Mary Ann H. T. Bigelow.
Read in English by Rachel; Lily Marie; Michael6230; Diana Schmidt; BettyB; Julia Niedermaier; Anusha Iyer; Jude; Liz Trollinger; Octavia Rosko; Lewis-James Mordieu; Leonard Wilson; Ian King; Jael Baldwin; Kalynda; Mike Pelton
This is a volume of poems by Mary Ann Bigelow, who turned her historical research into a poem in "the Kings and Queens of England". This volume also contains many of her other poems, most of which are dedicated to family members. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
